      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WHISKY POINT (3) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at Ballarat over 390m (22.16), scoring by a neck. Looks the one to beat. BLACK NEVERA (5) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.5 lengths (22.62) behind Paw Drogo at this track. Leading player again. NACHO PROBLEM (7) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 5 lengths into third (22.82) at this track in a Grade 5 over 400m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Must be included in calculations. PRINCESS DOMI (2) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
